title: Hour 3 - Stefon Diggs, Greg McElroy
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Stefon Diggs, Greg McElroy
description:
Dan sits down with Buffalo Bills wide receiver Stefon Diggs ahead of their Thursday night showdown against the Super Bowl champion Los Angeles Rams. He also talks to Greg McElroy about the college football season and college playoff expansion.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
